{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"concat","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/concat","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>concat</code> 関数は 2 つ以上の文字列を連結し、その結果として得られる文字列を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">concat(<em>string<sub>1</sub></em> ,<em>string<sub>2</sub></em> [,<em>string<sub>n</sub></em>]* )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"stringn\"><code><em>string<sub>n</sub></em></code></dt>\n <dd>この関数は 2 つ以上の引数を受け入れます。それぞれの引数は文字列です。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>関数に引数として渡されたすべての文字列を連結した、単一の文字列。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-concat\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko での対応","isH3":true,"content":"<p>対応済み。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"concat 関数は 2 つ以上の文字列を連結し、その結果として得られる文字列を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"concat","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"concat","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"concat","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"concat","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/concat"